svg.title: Pathway
svg.text: Individual is in their own thoughts, but engaged with a social media channel as a “downtime” activity. Fears and barriers are holding them back from actively seeking help.
That app tackles those fears by a combination of short stories with illustrations demonstrating positive outcomes and short information passages in plain english
The individual has read enough for now, and closes the app to get on with other things
An incident occurs which reminds the individual of the pressures of their situation so they decide to look at the app again
